<item>
            <title>[LU-12820] obd_dirty_transit_pages is always zero and can be removed</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12820</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &apos;transient&apos; arg to osc_enter_cache_try is always zero.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;OBD_BRW_NOCACHE is never set.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;obd_dirty_transit_pages and -&amp;gt;cl_dirty_transit are always zero.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So these and related code can all be removed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
